<HEAD>Bright &amp; Brief</HEAD>
<DATELINE>FREMONT, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Beware, shadetree mechanics of the 21st
Century: Don't try fixing your spaceship in your Fremont backyard.
   A reference to spacecraft popped up Monday when city officials
got a look at a revamped version of the city's vehicle repair
ordinance.
   The city used the definition of vehicle from Webster's New World
Dictionary. That identifies vehicles as ``vessels, aircraft and
